{
  "texts": [
    "This can be used along with historical data and domain knowledge to predict when failures would occur or how close they are to occurring.",
    "These methods have been used successfully in fault diagnosis of rotating machinery (Jiang et al., 2023), defect identification of stainless steel welds (Zhang et al., 2023), in monitoring and predicting the quality of solutions in electroplating (Granados et al., 2020), and in several other areas.",
    "While these methods provide excellent results in the real-world, they have limitations in terms of the types and formats of the data that can be used.",
    "Sensor signals and other measurements primarily take the form of numeric or image data.",
    "These methods are not equipped to handle text data, especially the technical text data from domain-specific maintenance operations."
  ]
}